node.accessibility_caption: Photo by @kaylanicolejones on August 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Remember: bad decisions don't make you a bad person. We all get triggered and go through moments of paroxysm. You are allowed to forgive yourself and grow if that'sno that' no longer who you want to be anymore! Don't let people take your dignity for being hurt and human.'.

node.text: Nobody knows your heart like you do 💖. (& God 😌) people hate when they can’t hang your faults over your head. I’m glad I was gifted that power.
